<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" i18n:domain="pyams_app_msc">
<head>
	<title i18n:translate="">
		[<tal:var i18n:name="service_name" tal:content="settings.service_name">Service name</tal:var>]
		New session request
	</title>
	<meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<style>
		html,
		body,
		p,
		pre {
			font-family: Ubuntu, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
			font-size: 13px;
			color: #333;
		}
		pre {
			border-left: 2px solid #346597;
			padding-left: 10px;
		}
		pre.noborder {
			border-left: none;
			padding-left: 0;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<p i18n:translate="">Hello,</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">
		You have received a new session request from <span i18n:name="sender" tal:content="sender.title">sender</span>
		(<span i18n:name="establishment" tal:content="profile.establishment">establishment</span>), based on the
		following criteria:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li><span i18n:translate="">Activity:</span> ${data.movie_title}</li>
		<li><span i18n:translate="">First proposed date:</span> ${data.start_date_1.strftime('%c')}</li>
		<li tal:define="start_date_2 data.start_date_2" tal:condition="start_date_2">
			<span i18n:translate="">Second proposed date:</span> ${start_date_2.strftime('%c')}
		</li>
		<li tal:define="start_date_3 data.start_date_3" tal:condition="start_date_3">
			<span i18n:translate="">Third proposed date:</span> ${start_date_3.strftime('%c')}
		</li>
		<li tal:condition="audience is not None">
			<span i18n:translate="">Audience: </span> ${audience.name}
		</li>
		<li><span i18n:translate="">Nb participants:</span> ${data.nb_participants}</li>
		<li><span i18n:translate="">Nb accompanists:</span> ${data.nb_accompanists}</li>
		<li><span i18n:translate="">Nb groups:</span> ${data.nb_groups}</li>
		<li><span i18n:translate="">Cultural pass:</span> ${'oui' if data.cultural_pass else 'non'}</li>
	</ul>
	<p tal:condition="data.comments"
	   i18n:translate="">
		<span i18n:name="sender" tal:content="sender.title">sender</span> added the following message to his
		request:
	</p>
	<pre tal:condition="data.comments"
		 style="padding: 5px 20px;">${data.comments}</pre>
	<p i18n:translate="">You just have to reply to this email to contact the request sender.</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">Thank you.</p>
	<br />
	<pre class="noborder" tal:content="settings.signature">signature</pre>
</body>
</html>
